                    <span>...I would come back from my grave to personally scalp the person who dared to illustrate my books with photos taken at all the low points of my live and dares to comment on these as Richard Smitten has done.<P>It is interesting to see at Amazon.de that there actually exists a German translation of a book in which the also famous Richard Wyckoff interviews Jesse Livermore.<BR>Why not publish the English original also ???<P>Note: as most will know, Reminiscences of a stockoperator is also based on interviews with Jesse Livermore, first published in Saturday Evening Post of 1922-1923.</span>
                  
              
